-- Marvel jumps on acquisition by Disney
-- 
-- Mon Aug 31, 2009 9:19am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/08/31/us-markets-stocks-beforethebell-marvel-idUSTRE57U2YM20090831

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of Marvel Entertainment soared more than 25 percent in premarket trade after Walt Disney Co announced it will acquire the company and its library of characters including Spider-Man, Iron Man and the X-Men. 

 Marvel shares last traded at $48.40, up 25.2 percent from their closing price on Friday. Disney shares closed at $26.84 on Friday. (Reporting by  Rodrigo Campos , Editing by Chizu Nomiyama)